1 (B) If payment of the renewal fee is postmarked on or
2 after July 16 sixteen (16) days after the expiration date of any given year,
3 the board may renew a license upon payment of the renewal of license fee plus
4 a late renewal payment penalty, which shall equal the amount prescribed for
5 late penalty per month under ยง 17-100-308.
6 (C) A license renewed under this subsection becomes
7 effective on the day after the request for renewal is postmarked.
8 (2) A person who requests renewal of a license, whose license
9 has expired, shall not be required to submit to examination as a condition to
10 renewal.
